/*
  Flyy Reflections Stylesheet
  This stylesheet defines the look and feel for the Flyy Reflections digital art studio website.
  Colors, typography, and layout draw inspiration from the brand's luxury hood aesthetic: bold pinks,
  cool blues, chrome accents and rich blacks. Forms and buttons are styled to be easy to use on
  both desktop and mobile.
*/

